.DS_Store
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Override any user-global gitignore that hides skill metadata files.
# Without these negations, files like AGENTS.md can exist locally yet be
# invisible to CI, which causes `validate-all-skills.sh` to pass locally
# and fail on GitHub Actions.
!AGENTS.md
!**/AGENTS.md

# Commit the repo-local Codex hook scaffold even when a user-global gitignore
# hides .codex/** for personal machine config.
!.codex/
!.codex/**
